Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From our beginnings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就力图拓展自己的领域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the human race has endeavored to extend our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们在走向最后的边界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And nowwe're headed for the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该是两星物种\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We should be a two-planet species.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从月球上的前哨站到火星上成熟的殖民地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From an outpost on the Moon to a full-fledged colony on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会是个挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也会是个灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could also be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 我们在打造搭载我们的火箭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now, we're building the rockets to get us there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及生存所需的装备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the machines we'll need to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拥有当太空人的"料"吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you have the right stuff to join the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:00:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要两个Scotty和两个Spocks (星际迷航)\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l want two Scottys and two Spocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒计时已经开始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The countdown begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"宇宙:太空殖民"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"The Universe: Colonizing Space."
