Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第十三集 殖民太空\N[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 13of19 Colonizing.Space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殖民太空已不再是科幻小说里的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Colonizing space is no longer the stuff of science fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似将生活在另一个世界里的第一批人类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's likely the first humans who will live on anotherworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经诞生在了地球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have already been born on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这些开拓者来说 这种冒险就会是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For these pioneers, this adventure will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终极宇宙野营\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the ultimate cosmic camping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你须带上你需要带上的所有东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You need to bring everything you need with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你须带上居所\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You need to bring a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你须带上吃的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You need to bring food you're going to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你须带上喝的水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You need to bring the water you need to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上 至少你无须带上呼吸的空气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now on Earth, at least...you don't need to bring the air you breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 一旦进入太空 我们同样必须带上它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but when we go into space, we'll need to bring that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须随身携带所有东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everything we need has got to be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果丢了什么 坏了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf something's missing or if something breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将会大难临头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it could be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要带上用得到的每一样东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We need to have everything we're going to use with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要使其发挥作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We need to have it working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功的太空殖民将取决于它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The success of space colonization will depend upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外头安家的野心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ambitions to settle somewhere out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直击我们生存的核心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}go right to the core of our existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殖民太空无法抗拒的理由\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The compelling reasons to colonize space...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是看我们能否将活动范围拓展到地球以外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are to see if we can expand the range of our activities beyond the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我们真的被局限在了地球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or are we really confined to the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那是我们需要得到答案的重大问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l think that's an important question...we need to know the answer to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二个问题是 生活的作用是什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The second one is, what's the role of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在地球上管这种现象叫生活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have on this Earth a phenomenon called life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否注定要拓展到地球以外去呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ls it destined to spread beyond the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是可以使其拓展的物种\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are the species that can cause that spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔·萨根 著名天文学家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Carl Sagan, the great noted astronomer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾说过 我们该是两星物种\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}once said that we should be a two-planet species.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们应该殖民一个星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That is, we should colonize one planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时还拥有地球 因为 比如\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and also have the Earth because, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球身处宇宙射击场中央\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Earth is in the middle of a cosmic shooting gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彗星 流星四处乱窜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are comets and meteors whizzing all over the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千百年乃至数百万年来从未停止过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on a scale of hundreds to thousands and millions ofyears...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要一个备用的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we need a spare planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 将所有的生命只放在一个星球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because it's simply too precious to put all life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是太珍贵了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on simply one planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在广袤的太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the vastness of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个目的地脱颖而出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's one destination above all others...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杰出的殖民首选之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that stands out as prime real estate for colonization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星是太阳系的大奖\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars is the grand prize of the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是人类可以定居的最近的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's the closest planet which human beings can settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗最近的行星拥有生命和文明所有必需的资源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's the closest planet that has all the resources needed...for life and civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星 太阳的第四颗行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars, the fourth planet from the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它约地球的一半大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's about half the size of Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其与地球的最短距离约3500万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and, at its closest pass, is roughly 35 million miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古罗马人将其红色与战争联系在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ancient Romans associated its red colorwith hostility...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其命名为战神\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and named it after their god ofwar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 非但没有敌意 火星还是继地球之后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But farfrom hostile, Mars has the potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在的最友好的行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to be the most hospitable planet after the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气态外行星没有踏脚之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The gaseous outer planets offer no solid ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在内行星中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Among the inner planets...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水星太靠近太阳 酷热难当\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mercury is too scorchingly close to the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金星 尽管大小如地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and Venus, though similar to Earth in size...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为失控的温室效应 受到华氏870度的煎熬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is baked to 870 degrees Fahrenheit...by a runaway green house effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 其大气压力将压碎所有想成为移民的人类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt also has an atmospheric pressure...that would crush any would-be human settlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星也有自己的缺陷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars does have its own pitfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上它的气压极低\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt actually has extremely low atmospheric pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会造成你血液沸腾 然后冻结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which would cause your blood to boil and then freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是增压太空服可以克服那个危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But a pressurized spacesuit can overcome that danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然 火星很冷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And while it's cold on Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,典型的白昼温度在零下20到40度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with typical daytime temperatures 20 to 40 degrees below zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人类穿着适当的防护 不难生存下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}humans could easily survive, wearing proper protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键在于 这颗红色星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most important, the Red Planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有稠密的二氧化碳大气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with its carbon dioxide-rich atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎具有我们维持殖民地运行所必需的自然资源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}seems to have the natural resources we would need...to keep a colony running.
