Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为基本上能挽救我们生命的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The things that l think pretty much saved our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这些氧气呼吸器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are these oxygen breathing devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火警中 当然必须要快速开启\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and during the fire, of course, that had to go on quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是谁直接掌握了硬件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf anybody knows firsthand how the hardware...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括生命支持系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}including life support systems...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么能坚持在载人火星飞船上的人 就非他莫属了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will work on the spacecraft taking man to Mars, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上这一切都是不以为然的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Down here on Earth, you take so much for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道 我们在户外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, we're out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳光和新鲜空气围着你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the sunshine, the fresh air all around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道在太空中你不得不制造出来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, in space, you have to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须制氧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You've got to make the oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面你身处一个封闭的生态系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Up there, you're in a closed ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须尽量循环利用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have to recycle, you know, whatever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所在这边 设计极其简单\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the toilet itself is over this way...and it's a very simple design.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 小解 尿液收集\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For example, we'd take the urine, collect it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是利用一个小漏斗 小抽吸装置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}using a little funnel, little suction device.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管男女都撒尿在这个管子里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For the male orfemale urination is this tube here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会收集起来 将尿液转化成水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'd collect that up, we'd convert the urine into water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水再变成氧 我们会呼吸空间站上的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}water to oxygen, and we would breathe our urine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封闭生态系统里的尿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}inside that closed ecosystem of the space station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望大家对我们带你飞过时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l hope you've got a feel for the space station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对空间站有个感性认识\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as we flewyou through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新硬件还能提供清洁可靠的能源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}New hardware will also provide power from clean, reliable sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会保护红色星球的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're going green to the Red Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳能电池板在重返月球时会发挥作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Solar panels will do thejob on the return to the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在去火星的长途旅行中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the longerjourney to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要另一种能源了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will require another power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们启程去火星时 远离太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we get off to Mars, the solar insulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星上的阳光强度只有地球上的一半\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the intensity of sunlight at Mars is only about half that at the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 太阳能电池板效率不高\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so solar panels are less effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能要认真考虑在某些飞船上用上核能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We may have to think carefully about using nuclear power sources...in some of these spacecraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 人们正在认真思考月球上利用核能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and, in fact, people are thinking seriously...about nuclear power sources on the surface of the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以解决长久的能源 而不必担心在月球的黑暗期间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in order to generate long-term power and not have to worry...about the periods of darkness on the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因没有阳光而不得不携带蓄电池\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where you don't have sunlight...and you have to bring batteries up to store power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管用上了所有的新硬件 火星之旅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But despite all the new hardware, thejourney to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然充满着潜在的风险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will still have its share of potential hazards...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同涉足任何一个陌生的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like any trek to an unfamiliar place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设想你去野外露营 远离家门\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmagine you're on a wilderness camping trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远离你熟悉的环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the familiar surroundings that you're used to. and you leave home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你踏上了长途之旅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You go out on a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在的风险 危险:\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Potential dangers, hazards:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塌方 雪崩 迷路\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Rock slides, avalanches, getting lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装备坏了 会出现各种各样的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}equipment breakdown, all sorts of possible problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你还是会义无反顾 勇往直前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But you want to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备 出发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You prepare, you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是一场冒险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是一场灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往月球和火星 同样如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Going to the Moon and Mars is going to be like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你离开了熟悉的地球环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You leave the familiar surroundings of Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you go out in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在的问题 情况 设备故障\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}potential problems, issues, equipment breakdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在野营中可能碰到的许多类似的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}many of the same kind of problems...that you might have on a camping trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航员在火星上也可能会碰上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the astronauts might face on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会是一场挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会是一场灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could also be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航员会遭遇的主要危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A major hazard the crewwill encounter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将是零重力环境中的长期失重\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be prolonged weightlessness in the zero-gravity environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不费力 乔治\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Easy in, Georgie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 是啊 真的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除了平日的荷载\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Relieved of bearing its usual load...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体骨骼开始恶化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the human skeleton starts to deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磷酸钙流失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a loss of calcium phosphate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是骨强度关键的化学物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a chemical critical to the rigidity of bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨细胞数量会减少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the number of bone cells actually decreases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天24小时的漂浮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For twenty-four hours a day, you're floating...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得你的身体会在生理上聪明地适应新的环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and your body very smartly starts physiologically to adapt...to that new circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 为了对付这一情况 努力保持你的强度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, in order to counter that, try to keep your strength up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用上跑步机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l'd get on a treadmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天两次一小时时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Two one-hour periods a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让全身振奋起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's about all you can muster up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管那样 回来时只能达到升空前强度水平的65%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln spite of that, you know, came back at about sixty-five percent...of my pre-flight strength level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量肌肉萎缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A lot of muscle atrophy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤为关键的是 有约14%的骨质流失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and, more significantly, about a fourteen percent bone loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你 下半身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, hips, lower spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了太空中 漂浮不费吹灰之力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You get up in space, you're floating effortlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨骼不停地流失钙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the bone just keeps dumping calcium...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能是长期飞行中的捣乱分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that could be a showstopper on a long-duration flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回到地面后 唯有经过剧烈的体能训练\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt was only through intense physical training...after his return to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才可以将骨质流失从14%减到2%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that Linengerwas able to reduce his bone loss...from fourteen percent to two percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失重的体虚效应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The debilitating effects ofweightlessness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们踏足乃至殖民火星之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}remain an issue that must be addressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然是一个必须克服的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before we set foot on Mars, let alone colonize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续在研究解决之道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Research continues on a possible solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人期待着人造重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A lot of people have looked towards artificial gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是飞船一路盘旋而上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which means you spin the spacecraft up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终将获得重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you end up with a gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是帮助给你的骨骼加载\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that would sort of help load your bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在失重的情况下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because when you're in weightlessness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的血液在流动 骨骼没有了荷载\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}your fluids are shifting, your bones are unloaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每个月会损失2%的骨质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you lose about two percent ofyour bone mass per month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将是个很大的障碍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt would be a large hurdle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为为了让宇航员抵达火星时健健康康\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because in order for crews to be healthy when they arrive on Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要在整个航程中得到锻炼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they need to be strong for the entire trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前从未有人建造过旋转飞船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nobody's ever built a rotating spacecraft before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 谁都不想成为第一人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so nobody wants to be the first person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而多数人相信利用旋转飞船产生的人造重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But most people believe that some kind of artificial gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with a rotating spacecraft on the way to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不失为履行使命的方法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is actually the way to do the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星之旅还面临着太阳风的危害\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Missions headed for Mars also face dangerfrom solar storms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳释放出的高能粒子爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}High-energy particle bursts unleashed from the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会将毫无防备的宇航员命丧九泉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could wipe out a crew ifthey aren't prepared for the onslaught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说辐射是一个不小的捣乱分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So radiation is one of the larger showstoppers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从技术上说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in terms of technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须开发出未来的航天器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that needs to be developed for a future vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最简单的处理方法就是制造一所风暴庇护所\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The easiest way to deal with that is just to make a storm shelter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 一旦你预测到太阳风暴来临了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that if you can somehow predict...when the solar storms are approaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你可以通过导航卫星从地球获悉的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which you would do with various navigation satellites...and relaying them from Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 你可以躲进庇护所 等其过去后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then you could get into the shelter and wait it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再回到飞船里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then be able to go back into the spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 火星上也一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then similarly on Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你获悉风暴将来临\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when you know that there's a storm coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以躲进庇护所\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you would go into a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光旅程就让殖民火星成为史无前例的挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thejourney alone will make colonizing Mars...an unprecedented challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是巨大的风险将换来历史性的回报\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the enormous risks come with historic rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不作决定比让谁去尤为重要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No decision is more important than who gets to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为你更称职当一名太空先驱吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Think you have what it takes to be a space pioneer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排队等候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已有人在接受训练了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are people already training for thejob.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殖民火星将需要特殊的人种\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Colonizing Mars will require a special breed of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于任务可能要持续两年多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With missions that could last more than two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遴选行星先驱的合格人选\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}selecting those with the right stuff to be planetary pioneers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.49,0:22:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是成功的关键所在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be critical to the success.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 1 点火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Two, one, we have ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射成本以数十亿计\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The cost of a launch, in the billions of dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧凑的航天器舱位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the tight quarters of the spacecraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将要求机组成员降低到最少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will keep the number of crew people to a bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为人数是四个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l believe that number is four.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你可以发送的最少人数\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's the smallest number you can send...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把机组分成两组\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and divide the crew up into two groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人是单独的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and have no one be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你发送的最少人数\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's the smallest number that you can send...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中需要有两种完成任务的主要技能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in which you have the two primary skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者相得益彰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the mission, both multiply backed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一组要包括两位机械能手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A crew of that size would consist of two ace mechanics...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会修理任何东西 这样才能挽救生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who can fix anything, and in doing so, save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外还有两名专业科学家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Joining them would be the two field scientists...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智力荷载\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the intellectual payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 按《星际迷航》的术语\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, in "Star Trek" terminology,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要两个Scotty和两个Spock\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l want two Scottys and two Spocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星殖民者需要的不仅仅是这些重要的技能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mars colonists will need more than just these vital skill sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还需要意志坚定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They also need to be mentally tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们认为宇航员很顽强\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People think that astronauts are tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只会永远服从命令 执行计划\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they will just always obey commands...and will operate according to plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他们也是人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but they are human...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在这种情况下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and humans in these situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实会产生怪异的心理反应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}do develop strange psychological reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.03,0:24:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们确实必须有所掌握\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We really have to understand that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 那是宇航员挑选过程的一部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because that's part of the crew selection process.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.54,0:24:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要飞进节点了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right, l'm going to fly into the node.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航员必须适应太空舱或密封舱狭小的空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronauts will have to adapt to the confined space...of the crewvehicle or habitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.71,0:24:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你患有幽闭恐怖症 就算了吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're claustrophobic, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.38,0:24:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 我们要测试的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We actually test for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.84,0:24:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会将你塞进一个球状物里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We put you in sort of a ball, zip it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.39,0:24:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面一片漆黑 你就塞在里面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's totally dark, you're crammed in the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在睡舱里 有一个小窗户\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnside the sleep cabin, there's also a little window...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.35,0:24:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡袋就放在里面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sleeping bag sitting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.19,0:24:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是指挥员睡舱的情形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This just happens to be the commander's sleep station.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.77,0:24:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会给你安上心脏监护器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they have heart monitors on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.15,0:24:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时睡着了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln my case, l fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.69,0:24:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们最后打开舱门 说 你不错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They finally came, opened the thing up, and said, "You're fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.32,0:24:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果你在密封空间里睡不着觉的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if you don't fall asleep in a closed space...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.91,0:24:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不是合格人选\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you're not the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.37,0:25:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为唯一的生命形式应对一个毫无生机的星球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dealing with being the only life forms...on an otherwise lifeless planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.08,0:25:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将是另一大心理挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be another major psychological challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.42,0:25:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外太空 你真的被人类开除了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Out there in space, you truly are just removed from mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.26,0:25:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道 我们生活中的交流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And, you know, the interactions we have in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.55,0:25:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同事 亲朋好友之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the colleagues, friends, family...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.43,0:25:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你视为理所当然的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}youjust sort of take it for granted down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.77,0:25:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 到了上面 突然之间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but up there, all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.39,0:25:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种孤独是我从未感觉过的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it is isolation like l've neverfelt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不自我感觉良好的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lfyou're not totally comfortable with yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.77,0:25:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将会在那里度日如年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you're going to have some very, very difficult times up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.61,0:25:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四个月了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's been four months...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.91,0:25:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四个月 模拟火星任务\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}four months, simulated Mars mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都表现出色\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everyone's doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.04,0:25:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了培训执行这个极端任务的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To train people for this extreme mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.21,0:25:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星协会建立了两个火星模拟研究站\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Mars Society has built two Mars analog research stations...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.79,0:25:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来实践模拟任务\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to practice simulated missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.97,0:25:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6人组成的小组\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Crews consisting of as many as six people...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.88,0:26:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分是大学里的科学家和航天局的工作人员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}mostly university scientists and NASA personnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.81,0:26:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的工作条件基本上如同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}operate under many of the same constraints...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.31,0:26:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航员在火星上坚持的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that astronauts will endure on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.31,0:26:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们出门就穿上航天服\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They don't go outside without wearing spacesuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.48,0:26:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们以火星时间作息 比地球昼夜要长出37分钟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They live on Martian time, 37 minutes longer than an Earth day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.32,0:26:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与丹佛指挥中心的通讯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their communication with mission control in Denver...
