Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.43,0:42:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们只会以我们破坏自己星球的方式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because we will just destroy things...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.93,0:42:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去破坏东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the way that we've destroyed our own planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.44,0:42:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要以科学研究的方式来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that we need to preserve the Moon and Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.77,0:42:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护月球 火星以及其他行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the other planets the way they are for scientific investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.82,0:42:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是否应该地球化火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whetherwe should terraform Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.95,0:42:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个留待后人去解决的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is an issue for future generations to resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是太空殖民历史长河里的一个遥远的时间点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a very distant point on a space colonization timeline...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.29,0:42:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能起步于我们这一代人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that could begin with this generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.63,0:42:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们或许能够预测的一件事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The one thing that we can probably predict...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.96,0:42:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们会自我审视\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that we will see ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.84,0:42:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于太阳系的其他行星要多于地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in other places of the solar system than the planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.97,0:42:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空殖民将通过正常的过程来推动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Space colonization will be driven...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.35,0:42:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到了在人类的历史上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by the normal processes that we've seen over human history...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.10,0:42:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们的扩张从一个地方到另一个地方 跨越边境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of expansion of people from one place to another, across frontiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.11,0:42:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空是另一种边境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Space is another kind offrontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.77,0:42:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是技术挑战的前沿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a technologically challenging frontier...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.11,0:43:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 人类贯穿历史一直是足智多谋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the human species has been extraordinarily resourceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.32,0:43:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类能够适应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}over its history in its ability to adapt...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.58,0:43:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并克服太空前沿之类的挑战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and to overcome challenges like the frontier of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.00,0:43:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子或许有朝一日将步老爸的后尘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My son, maybe someday, he'll follow in Dad's footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将会非常自豪 知道你已经勇往直前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and l would be awful proud knowing that you blazed the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.30,0:43:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你他会做到的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And, you know, he can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一代 谁知道他们会去哪？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The next generation, who knows where they'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.19,0:43:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空殖民将成为终极野营之旅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Space colonization will be the ultimate camping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.90,0:43:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它将会考验我们的设备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt'll test our equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.20,0:43:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考验我们的计划 考验我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it'll test our planning, it'll test us...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.74,0:43:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这将是值得的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it'll be worth it...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.95,0:43:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去更好地认识太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to learn a lot about space...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.25,0:43:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的地球 以及我们自己\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about our own Earth, and about ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.59,0:44:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是发生在火星上还是其他什么地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whether it happens on Mars or somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.51,0:44:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃至超出我们的太阳系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}maybe even beyond our solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.22,0:44:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空殖民的动力将不只是希望插上一面旗帜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}space colonization won't be driven by the desire to plant a flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.72,0:44:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是一颗种子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but rather a seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.23,0:44:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未来 当我们注目天堂发问\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the future, when we gaze into the heavens and ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.02,0:44:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"ls anybody out there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.52,0:44:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答将有可能是 "有 是我们"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the answerjust might be, "Yes. lt's us."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.00,0:44:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部分 是因为 这听上去非常地科幻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}partly because it sounds very science fiction-y...
